The Expense Tracker is a simple web application built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to help you manage and keep track of your personal expenses. It allows you to add, remove, and view your expenses, providing a simple way to control your spending and gain insights into your financial habits.

By the end of this project, you'll have a functional web application that allows you to:

Add new expenses
View a list of all expenses
Remove expenses when necessary
Track the total amount of expenses



